cu.explanation_en: Setting tr_s_preference to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause transport layer configuration errors, preventing proper F1 interface communication between CU and DU.

du.explanation_en: Setting tr_n_preference to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause transport layer configuration errors in the L1 layer, disrupting the connection between L1 and MAC layers.
du.explanation_zh: 將 tr_n_preference 設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致 L1 層的傳輸層配置錯誤，干擾 L1 和 MAC 層之間的連接。
